  "body": "**Description**\r\nethstats status updates are reported every second instead of every 15 seconds as is standard across geth erigon and besu. this spams the logs of the server full. i dont consider it as an ethstats server issue as the other clients arent causing it.\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n1. configure ethstats server (https://github.com/goerli/ethstats-server)\r\n2. configure nethermind to use ethstats server\r\n3. observe log spam on ethstats server\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\nnethermind reports its status to the server every second\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nnethermind reports ist status to the server every 15 seconds\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nnone\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - Operating System: not relevant\r\n - Version: 1.20.4\r\n - Installation Method: not relevant\r\n - Consensus Client: not relevant\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n1 second per update is overkill. i recommend making the default 15 seconds and offering an option to configure it if higher update rates are required.\r\n\r\n**Logs**\r\n```\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:10:59.764 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:00.765 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:01.764 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:02.765 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:03.768 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:04.764 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:05.765 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:06.766 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:07.764 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:08.766 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\nethstats  | 2023-09-27 07:11:09.765 [API] [STA] Stats from: EthStaker1-0x2c84f4abf289593affa64c7756a689898772f365d2619766567fa65e0082780d\r\n```\r\n",
